[Black "Chapter 9 Morphy Defense"]

{Only after ...Bc5 does Black aim for ...Nge7 and O-O, rendering Bg5 less effective. White responds with e5, intending Ne4 to follow.}

1. e4 c5 2. d4 cxd4 3. c3 dxc3 4. Nxc3 Nc6 5. Nf3 e6 6. Bc4 Bc5 {[%entry]} 7. O-O Nge7 8. e5 O-O (8... d5 9. exd6 Bxd6 (9... Qxd6 10. Ne4 Qxd1 11. Rxd1) 10. Qe2) 9. Ne4 b6!? (9... Bb6 10. Nd6) 10. Bg5 (10. Nxc5 bxc5 11. Be3) 10... h6 11. Nf6+ Kh8 (11... gxf6 12. Bxf6) 12. Bd3 *

